cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.CR 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with face recognition. The use of subspace learning and batch OHNM suggests that it may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) sub-category. The mention of efficient image retrieval and noise removal suggests that it may also belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories. Finally, the mention of bad local minima suggests that it may also belong to the cryptography and security (cs.CR) sub-category.
